    <item>
      <title>外汇损失抵消强劲的旅游需求，靛蓝航空利润未达预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/indigo-s-profit-misses-estimate-despite-strong-travel-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[InterGlobe Aviation Ltd. 是印度市场份额最大的航空公司，该公司报告称季度利润低于预期，原因是外汇相关损失增加抵消了在旅游需求强劲的时期运送更多乘客所带来的收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/indigo-s-profit-misses-estimate-despite-strong-travel-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 10:43:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
